{"article_id":"9349jIeXEbfbSRgd","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Republicans delayed a Senate Judiciary Committee vote on the Supreme Court nomination of Brett Kavanaugh this week","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to take Dr. Christine Blasey Ford up on her offer","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"to share with the panel her allegations","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that he sexually assaulted her in high school .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Then , late Tuesday , the 51-year-old research psychologist changed her tune ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"she does n't want to testify","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"until the FBI looks into her claims .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"`` If she is not going to be part of the hearing","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that would be a very interesting and unfortunate turn of events , ''","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"remarked Sen. Lisa Murkowski","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"( R-AK ) .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Democrats have also pushed for an FBI investigation ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"it 's `` essential ''","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to guarding the integrity of Monday 's proceedings .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` The FBI should be given time","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to reopen its background check on Judge Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"to speak to any potential witnesses or any relevant individuals , ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"told his colleagues on the Senate floor Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` That way , senators will have necessary information and expert analysis at their disposal at the hearing","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"making it much less likely that it will devolve into a","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"'he said ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"she said '","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"affair , ''","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Sen. Patty Murray","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"( D-WA )","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"she too thought","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"an FBI probe was necessary","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to avoid a repeat of the Anita Hill hearings nearly three decades ago .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"`` I came here","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"because of how Anita Hill was handled","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and the one thing","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"I do know","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"is that committee members need to have the facts , ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` That 's why they 're asking for an FBI background investigation .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"And I believe","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that that would produce a much better hearing . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"But Senate Judiciary Chairman Chuck Grassley","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"( R-IA )","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"says","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"the idea of an FBI investigation is closed","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"- and nothing","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"the intelligence agency does","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"would have any bearing on what Ford tells the committee .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"`` The FBI should n't be involved","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"because they do n't want to be , ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"the president said earlier this week .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"`` This is not really their thing .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"politically speaking","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"the senators will do a very good job . ''","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"While Judge Kavanaugh says","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"he 's ready to share his story on Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Dr. Ford has not agreed to either a private or public hearing with the committee .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"In the meantime , the Senate panel has also reached out to Kavanaugh 's friend , Mark Judge ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"whom","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Ford says","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"was in the room during the alleged incident .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"But Judge refused to appear ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"saying in a statement","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"he has no memory of the alleged assault","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"and never witnessed Kavanaugh acting in the manner","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Dr. Ford describes .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Meanwhile , evangelist Franklin Graham tells News","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"he thinks","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"the allegations are a tactic","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"to keep conservatives off the bench","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"and that people should n't be targeted for something","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"they did as a teenager .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` This is an attempt","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to smear him , ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Graham charged .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"`` They could n't find anything else on his record","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"and so this is just an attempt","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"to smear him","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"and smear his name","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"and put a black dot on it . '' `` I hope","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"the Senate is smarter than this","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"and they 're not going to let the process stop moving forward","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"and confirming this man , ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Grassley 's office says","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"the invitation","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"for Dr. Ford to testify on Monday","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"still stands ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"reiterating","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"that nothing","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"the FBI does","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"would have any bearing on what she tells the committee ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"and as such , there is no reason for any further delay .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":193,"left":0,"right":192,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":153,"right":191,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":108,"right":152,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":104,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":100,"right":103,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":100,"left":1,"right":99,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":2,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":5,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":6,"right":101,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":105,"right":106,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":123,"right":151,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":111,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":13,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":14,"right":109,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":109,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":116,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":113,"right":115,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":17,"right":112,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":114,"right":22,"relation":"same-unit","n